attributionInfo.brokerName: THE REAL ESTATE GROUP OF FAYETTEVILLE
THE REAL ESTATE GROUP OF FAYETTEVILLE

data.description: This beautiful home is tucked in the back of a cul-de-sac & the lot size spans over .70 acres. With a double car garage and a carport, the options for parking at your new home, abound! The landscaped walk way is a great introduction to the open foyer. The primary suite is directly at the front of the home for convenience. The living room is warmed by gas logs and leads into the formal dining room, and into the open kitchen. Upstairs, there are two bedrooms, a bonus room and a bathroom with two sinks situated opposite each other for convenience. The catwalk stairway allows you to keep an eye down below while moving about the ample storage closets and wide hallways upstairs. The backyard is no exception to the meticulous care and design this home brings with a permanent gazebo, garden and storage shed. The privacy of this backyard is unmatched! With a new roof installed in 2018, granite kitchen countertops and custom tile work, the improvements are just waiting for your special touch!
